sequenceDiagram
    participant I as Issuer<br/>(Real Estate Co.)
    participant P as Platform Backend
    participant K as KYC Provider<br/>(Sumsub)
    participant DD as Due Diligence<br/>Services
    participant L as Legal Services
    participant BC as Ethereum<br/>Blockchain
    participant C as Compliance<br/>Module

    Note over I,C: Phase 1: Issuer Onboarding
    I->>P: Submit issuer application<br/>(company details, docs)
    P->>K: Initiate corporate KYC/AML
    K-->>P: Corporate verification passed
    
    Note over I,C: Phase 2: Asset Due Diligence
    I->>P: Upload property documents<br/>(title deed, appraisal, insurance)
    P->>DD: Request property appraisal
    DD-->>P: Appraisal report: $10M value
    P->>L: Initiate SPV formation
    L-->>P: SPV LLC established<br/>(NewCo LLC)
    
    Note over I,C: Phase 3: Smart Contract Deployment
    P->>BC: Deploy RWA Token Proxy
    BC-->>P: Token contract: 0x1234...
    P->>BC: Deploy Compliance Module
    P->>C: Configure compliance rules<br/>(US only, accredited investors)
    
    Note over I,C: Phase 4: Token Initialization
    P->>BC: initializeToken(<br/>  name: "NYC Commercial Tower",<br/>  symbol: "NYCT",<br/>  maxSupply: 100000<br/>)
    P->>BC: Set issuance parameters<br/>(price: $100, period: 30 days)
    
    Note over I,C: Phase 5: Issuer Setup Complete
    P->>I: Asset tokenization complete!<br/>Dashboard access granted
    P->>BC: Mint initial allocation<br/>to issuer (for testing)
    P->>P: Schedule subscription period<br/>(starts: 2024-03-01)